Frequently Asked Questions

A few common questions from solo professionals before they get started.

1. Is there any setup fee?

For this offer, no. Your setup, design, and integration are included in the ₹ 4499/month (Billed Annually) or ₹ 5499/month (Billed Monthly). If your needs are more complex, we’ll discuss options upfront.

2. What if I already have a domain name?

Great. We can connect your existing domain to your new website. If you don’t have one, we’ll help you choose and register a suitable domain (domain cost extra at actuals).

3. Is ₹ 5499/month really enough to cover everything? What’s the catch?

There’s no catch. We standardised this offer around very focused websites (1–3 pages) and a streamlined setup so we can keep costs low and pass on the benefit to you.

4. How long will it take to go live?

In most cases, your site, email, and booking system are live within 5 business days after we receive your completed intake form and content.

5. Can companies purchase this service, or is it only for individuals?

Absolutely! Both companies and individuals are welcome. As long as the features in your chosen plan meet your needs, you're good to go—whether you're a solo professional or an established business.

6. What about future updates and new features?

All users, existing and new, receive future updates at no extra cost. When we add new tools or services to your plan, we'll notify you by email and activate them automatically. You get the benefits without paying more.

7. I don't want Google Workspace. Are there alternatives?

Yes! We offer Titan Email as a free alternative at no additional cost. Simply request Titan Email after placing your order, and we'll swap it in place of Google Workspace before setup.

8. What happens if I need more than 5 or 10 changes in a month?

Minor updates like image swaps, text edits, form tweaks, and code injections don't count toward your limit. For efficiency, we recommend batching your changes together so we can implement them all at once and deliver faster results.

9. Do I need to know anything about websites or tech?

Not at all. You give us your details, we design, set up, launch, and maintain everything. You just share the website link with your clients.

10. What about my existing Gmail or Yahoo email?

We’ll create a professional Google Workspace email for you. You can still forward mails or gradually migrate your conversations over to the new address.

11. Can I cancel anytime?

Yes, you can cancel at any time. Once cancelled, your hosting and managed services stop. You can request an export of your site at an additional one-time fee if you’d like to move it elsewhere.

12. Can you also help with marketing?

Yes. Beyond this starter package, AAPTA SOLUTIONS offers SEO, local search optimisation, social media setup, and paid ads management as separate services.
